Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域 往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气太不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？逆神隐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与神隐相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:53.65,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs16}神隱し；当一个孩子失踪之后很难找到或者找到后已经失去记忆，被认为是\N因为一些超自然的东西隐藏着他们（有可能进入了另一个时空），称为“神隱し”\N逆神隐就是有人突然神秘地出现（可能来自别的时空）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神殿被发掘出来…神降临了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样，神名君？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要发动“光之盾”就可以了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我想获取它的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们为什么要收留你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们得不到必须的数据\N你在这里就根本没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们为了吧你弄到这里\N付出了多大的代价吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀，没有责任感是一种罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无礼的小子！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是地球联合的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说，就是人类的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说人类不需要我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了，神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监察官，你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那位…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你护送王子殿下离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有些工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你把我说的当成命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你想自己试试是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试试？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道，你所有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在干什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了不就知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大扫除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还听老歌啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点来的话，我们就先吃过年面了，不等你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等olin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扑通…扑通…鸣响的心脏，摇曳的旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin…你还没有找到属于自己的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？在别人的家门口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会！我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远，他没对你做什么吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快进屋去，我们明天还要去海边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远也一起去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？\N什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海边…一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是羡慕，能去海边玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在是新年假期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这种异常天气还会持续二、三天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，今天在画久远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过画的真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看！我看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，画我怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当模特最适合了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！不行！我来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当模特更好对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦可马洪少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你的上司！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉制服就没什么上司不上司的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好！很久没较量了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！又是那个女孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了，没什么了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绫人君喜欢的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认输吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！不！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！吵死了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我学校的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.87,0:06:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这个女孩…和你…在这个世界的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里和东京相差12年，\N她在这里就是29岁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,29岁？那应该比你还大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与遥和如月博士一样的年纪…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你还记得MU大战前的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被植入的，不是真实的记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如月博士是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在是这样，\N总有一天我会想起来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱、梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信、无根据的幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你知道那首歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…\N我只想知道你喜欢不喜欢这首歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有这个资格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美屿怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…她不可能在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是对olin很重要的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她已经死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许吧，即使她活着…也应该是在东京的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在干什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个结界…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错…除了神名应该没有人能进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是地球联合的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是一个月前你才被派到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，你过去的经历不明…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查做得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感兴趣而以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方…我认识…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你只对如月博士感兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们会相处得很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我不是很有魅力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是个温柔的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样地…拒绝我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿，等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来女神的态度很坚决啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…那是最后一次见到他们吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，经过了4个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会派搜索队去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里待命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远！快回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛…他竟然和久远在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底怎么想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，真是巧遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个地方，这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个神祠是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生逆神隐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆神隐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，这里是38年前两个少女突然出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神隐本来是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸如“不想在这里，想到别的地方去”…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“想要远离现实一段时间”…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于那种想逃避现实想法\N而导致的神秘失踪事件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不可思议的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不少经历过神隐的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再返回后就又立刻消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，从此再也不会回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在发生神隐之前到底看到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来，有个很大规模的神隐事件呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是东京啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来，振作起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远小姐一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很快就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，你能先回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止搜索？你不担心吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失踪的不只是他！还有你妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放弃的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿啊？！老姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你要去哪儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个洞可真深啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！久远！你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.76,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo Jupiter？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那卵是转动时间的齿轮…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从里面会诞生出…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐惧…悲哀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往忘却的旅途…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那卵是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音…饱含着声音的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界所没有的旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有音乐才能创造出世界的新形态…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调律世界的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.15,0:17:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奏者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是olin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…伊修特利…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人君…？绫人君！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么“遥小姐”？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋！！人家都担心死了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊，遥小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？怎么天黑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊？！你失踪好几天了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，我进那个洞最多只有5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久远！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的吧…和东京
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我在里面看见Tokyo Jupiter了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，在听到歌声之后我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如你没听到，你会就那样回东京吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为会变得更有意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对，我已经保护好他们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过“绝对不会放弃的”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《Katun的宿命》…对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.17,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Katun：古代玛雅人的时间单位，1 Katun=7200天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.26,0:21:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿听过呢？好怀念…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么，很舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺高兴的，遥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做真的是为他好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从这里开始好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭档要互相多了解是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是聪明…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法忘却的过去  痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回响的旋律 轻轻掠过心间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon 第十乐章 记忆的奏鸣曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音